  "page": "Hammer (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Hammer\" title=\"Hammer\">Hammer</a></b> is a blacksmith and armorer for the Second Sons. It can also refer to:\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hammer_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Baelor_Targaryen\" title=\"Baelor Targaryen\">Baelor Targaryen</a>, known as the Hammer.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Garth_V_Gardener\" title=\"Garth V Gardener\">Garth V Gardener</a>, known as the Hammer of the Dornish.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Hammer_of_the_Hills\" title=\"Hammer of the Hills\">Hammer of the Hills</a>, an Andal king.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hugh_Hammer\" title=\"Hugh Hammer\">Hugh Hammer</a>, a dragonseed during the Dance of the Dragons.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tristifer_IV_Mudd\" title=\"Tristifer IV Mudd\">Tristifer IV Mudd</a>, known as the Hammer of Justice.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hammer_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hammer_of_the_waters\" title=\"Hammer of the waters\">Hammer of the waters</a>, a Westerosi legend.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hammerhal\" title=\"Hammerhal\">Hammerhal</a>, the seat of House Cordwayner.</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/King_Robert%27s_Hammer\" title=\"King Robert&#39;s Hammer\">King Robert's Hammer</a></i>, a war galley.</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Warhammer\" title=\"Warhammer\">Warhammer</a></i>, an ironborn longship.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_hammer_and_the_anvil\" title=\"The hammer and the anvil\">The hammer and the anvil</a>, a song.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405211117\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.004 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 7/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:27209-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405211117 and revision id 254778\n -->\n",
